**(1) Translation into English:**

Wei Wu Hou, after successfully planning a matter and finding no minister could match him, returned from court with a pleased expression. Wu Qi stepped forward and said:  
“Have you ever heard the words of Chu Zhuang Wang, spoken to those around him?”  
Wu Hou asked: “What did Chu Zhuang Wang say?”  
Wu Qi replied:  
“Chu Zhuang Wang, after successfully planning a matter and finding no minister could match him, returned from court with a worried expression. Shen Gong Wu Chen approached and asked: ‘Your Majesty appears troubled — what is the matter?’  
Chu Zhuang Wang replied: ‘I have planned successfully, and no minister can match me — that is why I am worried. It is because of the words of Zhong Hui: “Among the feudal lords, those who find a teacher become kings; those who find a friend become hegemonic powers; those who find a rival survive; but those who think they are the only ones capable of planning will perish.” Now, given my own unworthiness, yet no minister can match me — does this not mean our state is perilously close to destruction? That is why I am worried.’  
Chu Zhuang Wang was worried, but you, Your Majesty, are pleased.  
Wu Hou stood in respectful hesitation, then bowed twice: ‘Heaven has sent you, Master Wu Qi, to correct my mistake.’”

